# Module: Domain Logic (packages/element)

## Context

Contains core domain logic for elements (business logic layer).

## Applies to

packages/element/**/*.ts

## Rule

- Encapsulate business rules clearly
- Avoid UI concerns (no React, no DOM)
- Prefer immutable data structures
- Use explicit types for all domain entities

## How to verify

- Ensure no React or DOM usage
- Check immutability (no direct object mutation)
- Validate domain types are well defined
